playstore_details.title: CryptoCurrency : Prices, News, Forum & Converter
playstore_details.description:
SEE REALTIME PRICES/HISTORICAL PRICES OF YOUR FAVORITE CRYPTOCURRENCY

Realtime prices are supported up to 100 cryptocurrencies based on MarketCap Value.You can change base currency (16 currencies are supported for now: USD ,EUR ,GBP ,CHF ,TRY ,SGD ,ANF ,NOK ,DKK ,SEK, AUD, CAD, BRL, INR, PLN, RUB) You can also sort cryptocurrencies by alphabetical order, gainers & losers.

With release of version 2.0, you can see more information about selected cryptocurrency by clicking them. 

You can see historical prices by clicking the cryptocurrency and selecting an interval (5 days, 2 weeks, 1 month and 1 year graphs are supported for now.) If you select a value in graph, just click somewhere in graph.

SEE LATEST CRYPTOCURRENCY NEWS

This app shows latest news and Reddit feed posts (r/cryptocurrency). If you want to see more information of the news, just click the news and select the browser. You can also refresh news by swiping down.

MAKE COMMENTS ABOUT YOUR FAVORITE CRYPTOCURRENCY

With release of version 2.0, Forum feature is activated. This means you can post, comment and reply about your favorite cryptocurrency. (Google/Mail sign-in required.)

CONVERT YOUR FAVORITE CRYPTOCURRENCY

Live Currency Converter is supported up to 100 cryptocurrencies and 90+ currencies, updated once in 30 seconds. You can convert a currency to three different currencies at the same time.



For now, English, French and Turkish are supported.


Note: Prices shown in the app may be different from other exchanges/websites. This app is not responsible for any trade action.

For news and Reddit posts, this app is using CryptoControl.io API
